<br>
&quot;True, Magicians can be evil, and can throw up dmg shields. And Shamans can be evil, and throw up buffs / SoW. But the thing about a druid, is they can buff themselves up (including SoW) AND they can put up dmg shields - essentially a combination of a Magician and a Shaman, making them more powerful than either one of them. And considering 40% of the newts are druids, it makes it that much harder to kill them. <br>
<br>
